Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海坊主就是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼小的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海坊主哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜歡這味道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好餓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要讓海坊主哥哥一個人待著呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是從以前開始留傳下來的規定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海坊主經常會感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是餓著肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寂寞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙火很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飯萊很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神楽舞也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人願意來陪他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想好好看看夜神樂舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飯菜也不要一個人吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵醬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也餓的不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你想吃的料理全都挑出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用只選一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想吃什麼都告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那麼瞪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對又寂寞又餓著肚子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何也無法置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說絕對不能看到海坊主嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是災難的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道海坊主是怎樣帶來災難的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子只是一個又小又寂寞的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叉小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 肚子非常餓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒辦法放著那樣的孩子不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請妳們助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是廚師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然要服從廚師長的命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳們 解 明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼壽喜燒風味的肉豆腐就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盛菜的鍋要準備更大的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,量也要足哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後做個乳蛋餅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳蛋餅是什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用派打底的料理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤出來就是一個圓餅 大家分著吃更好吃喊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一會兒我會放進烤箱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等烤好了 妳們就幫我拿出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸雞腿沾蜜柑醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小不點 你也喝酒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海坊主分給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你的心意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡...是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海坊主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被關進大海盡頭的狹間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直被關在這裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好餓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我...一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被關到那麼陰暗的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直餓著肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每隔一百年才能離開那裡一次來這裡玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對那孩子來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是夢幻般的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,度過的是夢幻般的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前也被關進過一個黑暗的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是餓著肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又孤獨又饑餓的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳蛋餅烤好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子就是海坊主嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵醬 這是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是乳蛋餅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和風濃香咖哩蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有南瓜還有培根
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:07:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有慢慢的蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香的味道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩粉是大老闆大人帶給我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表快嚐嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外皮鬆脆 裡面軟嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..嚐不出味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道 我能嚐出味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵醬 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 妳們這幫傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別人在拼命地跳夜神樂舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們倒是玩的開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜神樂已經結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有最重要的「海上春至」沒跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是休息時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我擅自做了這些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由我們都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐看到的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去把剩下的料理也端過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次和蘭丸也一起來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會難得 我們也嚐嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 神聖的氣氛都被毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒說不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的演出要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「海上春至」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快要結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子的夢幻時光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磯姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳讓我來做海味珍饌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太感謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願這片土地上的人們能安穩地度過之後的百年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我一起留下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 但是我必須回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是伴手禮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無花果派和蜜柑果醬派
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海坊主 這是我的寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最漂亮的虹櫻貝珍珠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你收下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次也要一起玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你們的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百年後再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百年以後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許 我已經不在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快離開海灘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯 非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人也會開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要走了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有那個必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能再見到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想再和你相見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待你長大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一定會再相見的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海坊主離去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儀式最終還是成功了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦喲 這不是鬼神嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來讓你停手的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你封印了葵的味覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很後悔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候我應該直接吃掉她的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你敢吃了葵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會把你吃得乾乾淨淨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從骨頭到靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你在這世界上留下一點痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你死了 所謂的「打發時間」的小伎倆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就永遠消支了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被鬼神殘忍地吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜了 鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我向葵醬問個好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐 妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳沒事 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是以前那個救了我的妖怪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼一直不肯告訴我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那並不只是我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確一直給妳送食物的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最早去看妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有準備了「最後的食物」的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不過是在那位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去準備改變妳命運的食物的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代為保護妳一段時間而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是大老闆大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來 我只是個 除了陪伴在葵小姐身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都做不到的無力的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有銀次 我才能變得這麼堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才得到這莫大的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是我活下去的希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵...小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要道謝的應該是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妳讓儀式成功進行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一定是當年那次邂逅的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頑強地活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來到這個隱世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現在我的面前..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太感謝妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到折尾屋之後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都因為接待了太多的客人而精疲力盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但所有人都對儀式的成功而由衷地開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還在恨著我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我逃避了這片土地的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有的擔子都扔給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的離開 對於這南方之地來說是一個很大的轉機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果就是津場木葵呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天神屋的大老闆什麼的 都行動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘭丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬萬沒想到海坊主會感到寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一直以為 海坊主只會帶來災難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而事實恰好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那遙遠彼岸的黑暗空間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每過一百年會打開一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洩露出會引發災難的污穢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果儀式成功
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海坊主就會得鎮壓污穢的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們避免了天災
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情 之前想都沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了津場木葵我們才知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這之後的儀式要變一變了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飽含對海坊主的感激之情 溫情地招待他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你趕快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的棲身之所已經不在這了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,津場木葵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能再見嗎？還能一起做料理嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想吃南方之地的黃瓜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 一定還能再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次有你們的幫助 真是太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折尾屋創造了創立以來的最高營業額
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我們來說這也是一次難得的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 天神屋和折尾屋居然也會有聯手的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 總感覺有點奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹活太往死理了 一點也不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 是個好的掌櫃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還比不上你就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旁邊看小涼小姐做事 您果然很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好向我學習 繼續精進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就會追上妳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共同營業大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次有意義的嘗試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次儀式的時候 也請務必再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我在那片田地裡種的番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望妳嚐一嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈 該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就能再見面了 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是服了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 大老闆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這片不熟悉的土地上這麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 大老闆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不向你報恩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我為妳做過什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是覺得被拐到了一個陌生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我現在明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的所有人都是懷著信念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認真工作的好妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天神屋有我無可取代的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說 是最重要的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 天神屋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:40.07,title,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在妖怪旅館有美味佳餚
Comment: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:09.79,songtitle,,0,0,0,,「知らない気持ち 」作詞、作曲：シンリズム，編曲：シンリズム、高野勲，主唱：中島愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:26.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}ねぇ　どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:31.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}慣れない手で作った苦さを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:36.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}思い出して　笑ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:39.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}遠くで暮らし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:45.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}戸惑ってた　店先までも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:50.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}今では私の街
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:57.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}静かすぎて　眠れない夜でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:23:05.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}平気よ　見えない糸があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:10.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}ここがどこだって　構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.93,0:23:14.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}揺れる風景とその手を取り
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:16.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}まだ　ちょっとだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:21.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}知らないあなたの気持ちに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.55,0:23:25.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}そっと　寄り添いたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:31.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}迷ってしまわないように
Comment: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:26.35,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}喂　為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:31.23,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}回想起用不習慣的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:36.53,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}創造的苦澀　卻好像在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:39.94,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}在遠方的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:45.80,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}不知所措地　來到的店門前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:50.19,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}現在也已是我的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:57.96,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}即便是太過寧靜　而不成眠的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:23:05.38,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}也沒事唷　因為有著看不見的絲線
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:10.90,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}就連這裡是哪裡　都不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.93,0:23:14.67,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}搖曳的風景並牽起那隻手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:16.51,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}還　只是有點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:21.34,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}不知道對於你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.55,0:23:25.46,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}想要悄悄地　靠近過去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:31.05,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}為了不會迷惘
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到招待客人的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到夕顏
